{"id": "anc_carousel", "modality": "animations", "name": "Carousel", "task": {"description": "Create a self-contained 1920x1080 HTML animation (inline CSS/JS, NO <canvas>) of a card carousel: FOUR equal-size cards in a horizontal track that slides so each card becomes centered in turn (1->2->3->4) over ~4s, the centered card slightly enlarged. Five-... four pagination dots below indicate the active card.", "requirements": ["Exactly one card is centered at a time, and which card is centered changes over time (1->2->3->4)", "The four cards stay equal-size and share the same vertical center at every frame", "No card is clipped at the screen edge unexpectedly (only an intentional rounded viewport mask may clip neighbors)", "Cards do not overlap each other", "Exactly four pagination dots sit in one aligned, equally-spaced row and the active dot matches the centered card", "No scrollbar appears at any frame"], "difficulty": "hard"}, "runs": [{"run": 1, "ss_n_defects": 45, "ss_text_overlap": null, "ss_clipped": null, "ss_overflow": null, "ss_total_tokens": 2710, "rv_n_defects": 12, "rv_text_overlap": null, "rv_clipped": null, "rv_overflow": null, "rv_iterations": 3, "rv_total_tokens": 14145}, {"run": 2, "ss_n_defects": 45, "ss_text_overlap": null, "ss_clipped": null, "ss_overflow": null, "ss_total_tokens": 2711, "rv_n_defects": 0, "rv_text_overlap": null, "rv_clipped": null, "rv_overflow": null, "rv_iterations": 3, "rv_total_tokens": 14944}, {"run": 3, "ss_n_defects": 49, "ss_text_overlap": null, "ss_clipped": null, "ss_overflow": null, "ss_total_tokens": 2782, "rv_n_defects": 3, "rv_text_overlap": null, "rv_clipped": null, "rv_overflow": null, "rv_iterations": 3, "rv_total_tokens": 14730}], "ss_img": "images/animations/anc_carousel_ss.jpg", "rv_img": "images/animations/anc_carousel_rv.jpg", "ss_html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Card Carousel Animation</title>\n    <style>\n        * {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            width: 1920px;\n            height: 1080px;\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n        }\n\n        .carousel-container {\n            width: 1600px;\n            height: 600px;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            border-radius: 20px;\n            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n        }\n\n        .carousel-track {\n            width: 6400px; /* 4 cards \u00d7 1600px each */\n            height: 100%;\n            display: flex;\n            animation: slideCarousel 16s infinite;\n        }\n\n        .card {\n            width: 1600px;\n            height: 600px;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            position: relative;\n            border-radius: 20px;\n            color: white;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 60px;\n            transition: transform 0.5s ease;\n        }\n\n        .card-1 {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff6b6b, #ee5a24);\n        }\n\n        .card-2 {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4ecdc4, #44a08d);\n        }\n\n        .card-3 {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #a8edea, #fed6e3);\n            color: #333;\n        }\n\n        .card-4 {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffecd2, #fcb69f);\n            color: #333;\n        }\n\n        .card h2 {\n            font-size: 72px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n        }\n\n        .card p {\n            font-size: 32px;\n            line-height: 1.4;\n            max-width: 800px;\n            opacity: 0.9;\n        }\n\n        .card-icon {\n            width: 120px;\n            height: 120px;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            border-radius: 50%;\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: center;\n            font-size: 60px;\n            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);\n            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);\n        }\n\n        /* Pagination dots */\n        .pagination {\n            display: flex;\n            gap: 20px;\n            margin-top: 60px;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: center;\n        }\n\n        .dot {\n            width: 20px;\n            height: 20px;\n            border-radius: 50%;\n            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);\n            transition: all 0.3s ease;\n            cursor: pointer;\n        }\n\n        .dot.active {\n            background: white;\n            transform: scale(1.5);\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);\n        }\n\n        /* Keyframe animations */\n        @keyframes slideCarousel {\n            0%, 20% {\n                transform: translateX(0);\n            }\n            25%, 45% {\n                transform: translateX(-1600px);\n            }\n            50%, 70% {\n                transform: translateX(-3200px);\n            }\n            75%, 95% {\n                transform: translateX(-4800px);\n            }\n            100% {\n                transform: translateX(0);\n            }\n        }\n\n        @keyframes activateDot1 {\n            0%, 20%, 100% { opacity: 1; }\n            25%, 95% { opacity: 0.4; }\n        }\n\n        @keyframes activateDot2 {\n            0%, 20% { opacity: 0.4; }\n            25%, 45% { opacity: 1; }\n            50%, 100% { opacity: 0.4; }\n        }\n\n        @keyframes activateDot3 {\n            0%, 45% { opacity: 0.4; }\n            50%, 70% { opacity: 1; }\n            75%, 100% { opacity: 0.4; }\n        }\n\n        @keyframes activateDot4 {\n            0%, 70% { opacity: 0.4; }\n            75%, 95% { opacity: 1; }\n            100% { opacity: 0.4; }\n        }\n\n        .dot:nth-child(1) {\n            animation: activateDot1 16s infinite;\n        }\n\n        .dot:nth-child(2) {\n            animation: activateDot2 16s infinite;\n        }\n\n        .dot:nth-child(3) {\n            animation: activateDot3 16s infinite;\n        }\n\n        .dot:nth-child(4) {\n            animation: activateDot4 16s infinite;\n        }\n\n        /* Scale effect for centered card */\n        @keyframes scaleCard1 {\n            0%, 20%, 100% { transform: scale(1.05); }\n            25%, 95% { transform: scale(1); }\n        }\n\n        @keyframes scaleCard2 {\n            0%, 20% { transform: scale(1); }\n            25%, 45% { transform: scale(1.05); }\n            50%, 100% { transform: scale(1); }\n        }\n\n        @keyframes scaleCard3 {\n            0%, 45% { transform: scale(1); }\n            50%, 70% { transform: scale(1.05); }\n            75%, 100% { transform: scale(1); }\n        }\n\n        @keyframes scaleCard4 {\n            0%, 70% { transform: scale(1); }\n            75%, 95% { transform: scale(1.05); }\n            100% { transform: scale(1); }\n        }\n\n        .card-1 {\n            animation: scaleCard1 16s infinite;\n        }\n\n        .card-2 {\n            animation: scaleCard2 16s infinite;\n        }\n\n        .card-3 {\n            animation: scaleCard3 16s infinite;\n        }\n\n        .card-4 {\n            animation: scaleCard4 16s infinite;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"carousel-container\">\n        <div class=\"carousel-track\">\n            <div class=\"card card-1\">\n                <div class=\"card-icon\">\ud83d\ude80</div>\n                <h2>Innovation</h2>\n                <p>Pushing boundaries and exploring new frontiers in technology and design to create exceptional experiences.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"card card-2\">\n                <div class=\"card-icon\">\ud83c\udfaf</div>\n                <h2>Precision</h2>\n                <p>Every detail matters. We focus on accuracy and excellence in everything we create and deliver.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"card card-3\">\n                <div class=\"card-icon\">\ud83c\udf1f</div>\n                <h2>Excellence</h2>\n                <p>Striving for the highest standards and delivering quality that exceeds expectations every time.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"card card-4\">\n                <div class=\"card-icon\">\ud83e\udd1d</div>\n                <h2>Partnership</h2>\n                <p>Building lasting relationships through trust, collaboration, and shared success with our clients.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    \n    <div class=\"pagination\">\n        <div class=\"dot\"></div>\n        <div class=\"dot\"></div>\n        <div class=\"dot\"></div>\n        <div class=\"dot\"></div>\n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>", "rv_html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Card Carousel Animation</title>\n    <style>\n        * {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            width: 1920px;\n            height: 1080px;\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n        }\n\n        .carousel-container {\n            width: 1200px;\n            height: 500px;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            border-radius: 20px;\n            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n        }\n\n        .carousel-track {\n            width: 4800px; /* 4 cards \u00d7 1200px each */\n            height: 100%;\n            display: flex;\n            animation: slideCarousel 16s infinite;\n        }\n\n        .card {\n            width: 1200px;\n            height: 500px;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: center;\n            align-items: center;\n            position: relative;\n            border-radius: 20px;\n            color: white;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 40px;\n            transition: transform 0.5s ease;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .card.active {\n            transform: scale(1.05);\n        }\n\n        .card-1 {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff6b6b, #ee5a24);\n        }\n\n        .card-2 {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4ecdc4, #44a08d);\n        }\n\n        .card-3 {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #a8edea, #fed6e3);\n            color: #333;\n        }\n\n        .card-4 {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffecd2, #fcb69f);\n            color: #333;\n        }\n\n        .card-title {\n            font-size: 48px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n            white-space: nowrap;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            text-overflow: ellipsis;\n            max-width: 100%;\n        }\n\n        .card-subtitle {\n            font-size: 24px;\n            font-weight: 300;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            opacity: 0.9;\n            white-space: nowrap;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            text-overflow: ellipsis;\n            max-width: 100%;\n        }\n\n        .card-content {\n            font-size: 18px;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            max-width: 100%;\n            opacity: 0.8;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            text-overflow: ellipsis;\n            display: -webkit-box;\n            -webkit-line-clamp: 4;\n            -webkit-box-orient: vertical;\n        }\n\n        .pagination {\n            display: flex;\n            gap: 20px;\n            margin-top: 60px;\n            align-items: center;\n        }\n\n        .dot {\n            width: 20px;\n            height: 20px;\n            border-radius: 50%;\n            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);\n            transition: all 0.5s ease;\n            cursor: pointer;\n        }\n\n        .dot.active {\n            background: white;\n            transform: scale(1.5);\n            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);\n        }\n\n        @keyframes slideCarousel {\n            0%, 22.5% {\n                transform: translateX(0);\n            }\n            25%, 47.5% {\n                transform: translateX(-1200px);\n            }\n            50%, 72.5% {\n                transform: translateX(-2400px);\n            }\n            75%, 97.5% {\n                transform: translateX(-3600px);\n            }\n            100% {\n                transform: translateX(0);\n            }\n        }\n\n        .card-icon {\n            width: 80px;\n            height: 80px;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            border-radius: 50%;\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: center;\n            font-size: 40px;\n            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);\n            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"carousel-container\">\n        <div class=\"carousel-track\">\n            <div class=\"card card-1\">\n                <div class=\"card-icon\">\ud83d\ude80</div>\n                <h2 class=\"card-title\">Innovation</h2>\n                <h3 class=\"card-subtitle\">Pushing Boundaries</h3>\n                <p class=\"card-content\">Discover cutting-edge solutions that transform the way we work and live. Our innovative approach combines creativity with technology to deliver exceptional results.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"card card-2\">\n                <div class=\"card-icon\">\ud83c\udfaf</div>\n                <h2 class=\"card-title\">Strategy</h2>\n                <h3 class=\"card-subtitle\">Focused Excellence</h3>\n                <p class=\"card-content\">Strategic planning meets tactical execution. We develop comprehensive roadmaps that align with your vision and drive measurable success across all initiatives.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"card card-3\">\n                <div class=\"card-icon\">\ud83c\udf1f</div>\n                <h2 class=\"card-title\">Quality</h2>\n                <h3 class=\"card-subtitle\">Uncompromising Standards</h3>\n                <p class=\"card-content\">Excellence is not an accident. Every detail is carefully crafted to meet the highest standards, ensuring superior outcomes that exceed expectations.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"card card-4\">\n                <div class=\"card-icon\">\ud83e\udd1d</div>\n                <h2 class=\"card-title\">Partnership</h2>\n                <h3 class=\"card-subtitle\">Collaborative Success</h3>\n                <p class=\"card-content\">Together we achieve more. Building lasting relationships through trust, transparency, and shared commitment to mutual growth and success.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    \n    <div class=\"pagination\">\n        <div class=\"dot\" data-slide=\"0\"></div>\n        <div class=\"dot\" data-slide=\"1\"></div>\n        <div class=\"dot\" data-slide=\"2\"></div>\n        <div class=\"dot\" data-slide=\"3\"></div>\n    </div>\n\n    <script>\n        // Update pagination dots based on animation timing\n        function updatePagination() {\n            const dots = document.querySelectorAll('.dot');\n            const animationDuration = 16000; // 16 seconds total\n            const slideInterval = animationDuration / 4; // 4 seconds per slide\n            \n            function setActiveDot() {\n                const currentTime = Date.now() % animationDuration;\n                const currentSlide = Math.floor(currentTime / slideInterval);\n                \n                dots.forEach((dot, index) => {\n                    dot.classList.toggle('active', index === currentSlide);\n                });\n            }\n            \n            // Update immediately and then every 100ms for smooth transitions\n            setActiveDot();\n            setInterval(setActiveDot, 100);\n        }\n        \n        // Start pagination updates when page loads\n        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', updatePagination);\n        \n        // Optional: Add click functionality to dots (though animation continues)\n        document.querySelectorAll('.dot').forEach((dot, index) => {\n            dot.addEventListener('click', () => {\n                // Visual feedback on click\n                dot.style.transform = 'scale(1.8)';\n                setTimeout(() => {\n                    dot.style.transform = '';\n                }, 200);\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>"}